title: Atlantean Syndra missing effects on her recall on the Howling Abyss
body:
https://youtu.be/nEDv7RibA0M?t=199

In this video, Atlantean Syndra has a vortex of water beneath her when recalling. On the Howling Abyss, it's not there and makes her recall look weird. I didn't get a video of it though, but I'll probably do that tomorrow.

replies.body:
Hey Ace of Eden,

Thanks for the report! We'll see what happened here and get it resolved ASAP! :]

Yeah I see it too http://postimg.org/image/4xtu7zgrp/
I mean it's not that big of a deal tho because we don't recall on the map
